                    <StackPanel Orientation="Vertical">
                        <TextBlock x:Name="subHeaderText" FontSize="14" TextWrapping="Wrap" Foreground="Black" Margin="10">
                       t’s never a bad time for dessert. Cookies, cake, pie, you name it! But sometimes you need to change it up with something a little fancier: enter macarons. They may seem intimidating but with our easy-to-follow guide, they don’t have to be. And you can customize them!
                        </TextBlock>
